asset.hookText: With a deep-reclining handle that helps you get under all your furniture, and its lightweight size, the WindTunnel Air vacuum makes cleaning your floors really easy. In this tutorial, we'll provide you with simple, clear instructions on how to put your vacuum together and make sure your brushroll is spinning.
